If you need a job done right, you ask for the experts. At D & K Heating Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning in Belleville, we’re passionate about performing quality HVAC repair and installation work. We even put it in writing. Our 100% Satisfaction Guarantee displays our commitment to upholding the highest level of heating and air conditioning services in the industry. As a matter of fact, D & K Heating Service Experts in Belleville repairs, sells and installs more heating and cooling systems than any other HVAC repair and service company in all of North America – more people entrust us with their home’s heating and cooling, so you can rest easy knowing your home is in good hands.

D & K Heating Service Experts in Belleville will take care of all your home comfort needs. Whether your air conditioner or furnace breaks on the day you need it most or you’re looking for indoor air quality solutions that have earned the highest EPA and ENERGY STAR® standards, you can rely on our Belleville team. We’re experts in heating and air conditioning, and superior service is what we do best.

We Know Furnaces – That’s Why D & K Heating Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning in Belleville is Your One-Stop Shop for All Your Furnace-Related Needs

We understand your comfort needs are top priority… and that everyone’s desires are different, which is why we’ve got you covered from the get go. Whether you want a new air conditioner or just need yours tuned up for the long haul, Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning of Belleville is here to serve all of your HVAC needs. Our experts are ready to help redefine the word comfort for you and your home. View our air conditioning services below and find the perfect fit for your needs, then schedule an appointment so we can get you back to relaxing in no time.

Our AC repair professionals understand that your patience can wear thin swiftly when the temperatures start rising, and no one likes being hot under the collar. Your comfort should never be threatened, which is why we’re available 24/7/365. Need a technician now? Call 613-707-2421 and we’ll be there in a jiffy. Don’t forget to check for coupons and current deals on our services as well.

We know a lot of work is involved in keeping your home comfortable. Between deciding to replace your furnace to scheduling maintenance and furnace repairs, D & K Heating Service Experts in Belleville has got you covered on all fronts. Seriously. Sure, service may be part of our name, but it’s not the only area we excel in. Just browse through all our categories below to find out just how well your furnace will be taken care of when you work with the experts.

Keeping your home comfy doesn’t have to be a hassle, either. We’re on call with live customer service 24/7/365, so you will hardly have to wait before our technicians arrive for a repair. Plus, we offer a 100% Satisfaction Guarantee on all our work. So call 613-707-2421 or schedule a free appointment, and don’t forget to look through our coupons to save on services and more.
products:
When you think about it, replacing your old furnace or air handler sounds like a no-brainer. You’ve made more than your share of heating repair calls recently, and you want consistent heat and a more energy efficient system. It’s not worth throwing all your dollars into our furnace repair service (but we’re not complaining) when you could have a new furnace or air handler that will save you money in the long run.

As a prior D & K Heating Service Experts customer in Belleville, you already know the benefits of working with us. However, we don’t only offer HVAC services – D & K Heating Service Experts also carries a variety of heating equipment. Even better, our professionals will work with you to determine the best product for your home, your needs and your budget. That’s fewer worries for you and more comfort for your family.

We offer a whole range of Lennox® furnaces and air handlers in Belleville. Discover more on our website or by scheduling a free appointment with one of our experts. Or, feel free to call 613-707-2421, too. We’re eager to work with you on all your furnace and air handler needs.
services:
FURNACE REPAIR SERVICE

Whether your unit stops working on your way to work or the middle of the night, our experts will be out to repair your furnace in no time. Our NATE-certified technicians have been through the most prestigious training and certification in the industry, so they’ll fix your problem correctly the first time. Our expert professionals at D & K Heating Service Experts in Belleville are trained to service any kind of furnace or boiler, so you can be certain you’ll get the best service around.

FURNACE SALES & INSTALLATION

Replacing your furnace is quite the task. How do you know where to begin? Don’t worry. Our expert heating and cooling consultants will help you figure out which unit is best for your specific home based on the size of your home, your family’s air quality requirements, financing budget and your desired energy efficiency. One of our experts will work with you every step of the way from choosing the best system and financing solution, to carrying out an expert equipment installation when it arrives.

FURNACES & AIR HANDLERS

If you’re searching for a replacement furnace or air handler, look no further than D & K Heating Service Experts in Belleville. We offer a wide selection of gas furnaces, oil furnaces, air handlers, boilers and garage heaters – and all our products boast high efficiency, low noise levels and, of course, durable performance. Look through our full range of products here.

FURNACE MAINTENANCE 

You can’t completely prevent your furnace from breaking down, but you can help thwart it with annual furnace maintenance visits. Our in-depth furnace tune-ups and PLUS service plans actually save in two ways. First, a well-maintained unit will perform more efficiently and uses less energy, which saves the environment. Second, proper maintenance means fewer costly repairs. We don’t know about you, but we’d rather spend that money on something else. And with lower utility bills, we can!

AC REPAIR SERVICE

AC Repair doesn’t have to be an annoyance. Sure, you’re probably not in your happiest moment when you need us, but rest assured, we’re here to take care of any AC repair issue that arrives. We’re certified to service all brands of air conditioners, so you know you’ll be getting the finest AC repair in Belleville. And with a written 100% Satisfaction Guarantee you have nothing to lose.
NEW AIR CONDITIONERS

The time has come to finally take the next step to updating your home’s air conditioner. Upgrading your current system is actually more affordable than you may think, so why delay? It’s as easy as scheduling a FREE estimate to learn what options you have. Just fill in your information and we’ll work with you to make your home cool, energy efficient, and the most comfortable it has ever been.
Air Conditioning Maintenance

So you’ve got your thermostat programmed perfectly but you’re still not satisfied with your energy bill every month? Much like cars, AC maintenance is critical to ensure your home is running at maximum efficiency. We’ve made four service plans to meet your particular AC maintenance need, in addition to your budget.
Solar Air Conditioning

We won’t inundate you with a bunch of “green” terminology, but you should know that solar air conditioning is a lot more reasonable and practical than you make think. We have countless products that can take your home to the next level of efficiency and also provide your wallet with a little more green as well. While you shouldn’t stare into the sun, you should definitely take a look into utilizing all the power it provides.

AIR CONDITIONERS

We all love being comfortable. Keeping your home cool plays a large part in your family’s comfort in the heat of the summer and we’re here to help ensure you preserve the level of comfort your need. Choosing one of our ENERGY STAR® qualified air conditioners will keep your home the ideal temperature while giving you a quiet and efficient system that helps lessen your carbon footprint at the same time.
specialities:
It’s time to consider taking steps to increase the quality of the air you breathe indoors. Doing so can:

    Maintain your health. That’s right. And actually, 50% of all illnesses are either caused or aggravated by polluted indoor air according to the American College of Allergists.
    Cut down your energy consumption. How? Cleaner air improves how efficient your heat and AC works. Can you say “smaller carbon footprint” and “lower costs over time?”
    Protect your investment. Better air quality keeps heating and air conditioning components from corrosion, microbials, dirt and debris.

If you’re a DIYer, you can certainly take steps to bump the air quality in your home. But even the most mechanically-minded homeowners can’t do it all… and that’s where D & K Heating Service Experts Heating & Air Conditioning comes in. With a complete offering of indoor air quality equipment choices, knowledge and expert service—for all makes and models, 24 hours a day—you can take that deep breath indoors and know it’s the highest indoor air quality possible.
